## 🏗 ACTUAL TECH STACK (what's already in the repo)

```
Runtime:      Node.js + TypeScript (ESM)
Frontend:     React + Vite + Wouter (routing) + TanStack Query
Backend:      tRPC v11 (type-safe API layer)
Database:     MySQL (Drizzle ORM + drizzle-kit migrations)
Auth:         Custom session-based auth (no NextAuth)
UI:           Radix UI + shadcn/ui + Tailwind CSS
Drag-drop:    @dnd-kit/core + @dnd-kit/sortable
PDF:          PDFKit
Storage:      AWS S3 (@aws-sdk/client-s3)
WhatsApp:     WhatsApp Cloud API (server/whatsappCloud.ts)
Monitoring:   Sentry (@sentry/node)
Testing:      Vitest + Playwright
AI/LLM:       OpenAI (server/_core/llm.ts)
Image gen:    server/_core/imageGeneration.ts
Voice:        server/_core/voiceTranscription.ts
i18n:         Custom (client/src/locales/, ~17 pages incomplete)
```

