- **Billing/Invoicing** — invoice generation, PDF export, buyer portal; MISSING: payment gateway, aging, dunning, credit notes
- **Analytics** — reports exist; MISSING: proper BI dashboards, cross-module insights
- **Automation** — automation_rules + logs tables exist; MISSING: visual builder UI, reliable execution engine

