### GAP 4: End-of-Service Gratuity Calculator [OMAN LABOUR LAW]
**File to modify:** `server/routers/payroll.ts`, `server/routers/hr.ts`
**What's missing:** Cannot offboard employees correctly without gratuity calculation.

```typescript
// CREATE: server/gratuityCalculator.ts
// Oman Labour Law (Royal Decree 35/2003, amended) gratuity rules:
//
// For employees with < 3 years service: NO gratuity (resignation)
// For employees with 3–5 years: 15 days basic salary per year
// For employees with > 5 years: 1 month basic salary per year
// For termination by employer: 1 month per year regardless
// For retirement: 1 month per year
// Maximum: no statutory cap in Oman (unlike UAE)
// Calculation base: LAST DRAWN basic salary only (not allowances)
// Partial years: pro-rated by days
//
// Function signature:
// calculateGratuity(params: {
//   hireDate: Date,
//   terminationDate: Date,
//   lastBasicSalary: number,  // OMR
//   terminationType: 'resignation' | 'termination' | 'retirement' | 'end_of_contract',
//   nationality: 'omani' | 'expat'  // Omanis on PASI — different rules
// }): { gratuityAmount: number, yearsOfService: number, breakdown: string }

// ADD to schema: employeeFinalSettlements table
// Fields: employeeId, terminationDate, terminationType, yearsOfService,
//         basicSalaryAtTermination, gratuityAmount, leaveEncashment,
//         otherDeductions, netPayable, status, approvedById, paidAt
```

